Revision history for Perl extension Net::NicoVideo

0.28 2013-11-04
  - "GINZA" is supported
  - Improve Net::NicoVideo::Content, API was changed, but it has no discernible impact on the interface with UA
  - Deprecete is_content_success and is_content_error on Net::NicoVideo::Response
  - Improve samples
  - Improve documents

0.27 2013-08-12
  - Short domain nico.sc is discriminable
  - Improve tests

0.01_25 2013-06-12
  - Improve document, Japanese split off
  - Tidy Makefile.PL

0.01_24 2013-06-09
  - Add Net::NicoVideo::URL to convert long URL and short URL mutually

0.01_23 2013-01-26
  - Fix bug, tag request cannot URI::Escape::escape \x{NNNN}
  - Fix sort order bug in fetch_tag_rss_by_recent_post
  - Add workaround in fetch_flv, because "so" does not use as video_id. Why?
  - Update README

0.01_20 2012-07-19
  - The first of public release

0.01 2011-11-23
  - Original version
